<document>
    <properties>
        <title>Install Tomcat</title>
    </properties>
    <body>
     <section name="Install Tomcat">
      <span class='shortdesc'>Learn how to install Apache Tomcat</span>
      <span class='to_index' id='Tomcat, install'/>

     <p>
      If you do not have Tomcat
      installed, there may be another servlet container or application server installed
      on your system, which you can use for Hippo CMS, see <a href='index.html'>here</a>.
      If you decide you want Tomcat, continue.
     </p>

      <div class='nav'>
       <table>
        <tr> 
         <td>
            Download 
     </td>
         <td> 
          <span class='download-48 icon-48'/> 
     </td>
         <td>Download <span class='index' id='tomcat_6.0'>Tomcat 6.0</span> 
           from the <a href="http://tomcat.apache.org/download-60.cgi">Apache Tomcat</a> website,
           or if you prefer, download <span class='to_index' id='tomcat_5.5'/><a href="http://tomcat.apache.org/download-55.cgi">Tomcat 5.5</a>.
     </td>
    </tr>
  <tr>
   <td>Unzip</td>
   <td>
     <span class='unzip-48 icon-48'/> 
   </td>
   <td>Unpack the zip. In the rest of this todo list, 
       the acquired tomcat folder will be called $TOMCATDIR. 
       It has a name like apache-tomcat-6.0.18.
   </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
   <td><a name='startup'/>Startup</td>
   <td>
    <span class='commandline-48 icon-48'/>
   </td>
   <td>
       Start Tomcat with one of the startup scripts in <code>$TOMCATDIR/bin</code>,
       .sh for Linux and .bat for MS.
   </td>
   </tr>

  <tr>
   <td>Web Browser</td>
   <td>
    <span class='web-48 icon-48'/> 
   </td>
  <td>
     Users can now open the local Tomcat site <a href="http://localhost:8080/cms/">http://localhost:8080</a> in 
     their browsers.
  </td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
   <td>Quit</td>
   <td>
    <span class='logout-48 icon-48'/>
   </td>
   <td>
     Quit Tomcat with one of the shutdown scripts in <code>$TOMCATDIR/bin</code>.
     .sh for Linux and .bat for MS.
   </td>
  </tr>
   </table>
  </div>


     </section>
    </body>
</document>
